  "readme": "# mbedtls\n\nMbed TLS is a C library that implements cryptographic primitives, X.509 certificate manipulation and the SSL/TLS and DTLS protocols\n\n## Installation\n\nAdd to your `dfetch.yaml`:\n\n```yaml\nprojects:\n  - name: ext/mbedtls\n    url: https://github.com/ARMmbed/mbedtls\n    tag: v3.5.2\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAfter running `dfetch update`, the library will be available at `ext/mbedtls/`.\n",
